reviews:
while passing through paris i tested this games bar quite randomly, i was pleasantly surprised, we had a great evening :)
they even managed to give me good advice, me who never knows what to play, thank you!; you are looking for a place to relax with family, friends or colleagues, discover (or replay) board games in a good atmosphere, i recommend play in. the room is bright, spaced out, with plenty of choice of games, and the entertainment team is on hand to take care of you.; a top games bar, with a team that is super available and attentive.
we feel that they are truly passionate!; a spacious and warm room with a wide range of freely accessible games!; too nice! :)
